Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.34,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fad(310,200)\an4\fs30\bord0\shad2\1c&HFFFFFF&\move(760,170,770,170,100,3700)}16时12分／樱木町站前广场附近2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:14.03,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fad(310,200)\an4\fs30\bord0\shad2\1c&HFFFFFF&\move(105,170,115,170,100,3700)}16时14分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,特尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,已经知道敌人的真面目了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,藏在敌人装甲车内  经过真田鉴定  是魔法增幅器
