Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法增幅器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.31,UpText,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,660)}Sorcery Booster
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,由无头龙供给的魔法增幅装置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:42.69,UpText,,0,0,0,,{\pos(483,660)}No Head Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人果然是大亚联合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你才刚刚汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但车站前的广场有民间人士准备了难民撤离用的直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在要赶往车站掩护撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.21,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fad(310,200)\an4\fs30\bord0\shad2\1c&HFFFFFF&\move(105,170,115,170,100,3700)}16时33分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.51,Notice,,0,0,0,,樱木町站入口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,救援直升机来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的任务也快完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,下一波要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:34.53,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fad(310,200)\an4\fs30\bord0\shad2\1c&HFFFFFF&\move(100,170,110,170,100,3700)}16时34分／樱木町站前广场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,总算可以避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,化成体？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,达也？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.66,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fad(310,200)\an4\fs30\bord0\shad2\1c&HFFFFFF&\move(142,170,152,170,100,3700)}16时51分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:35.51,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fad(310,200)\an4\fs30\bord0\shad2\1c&HFFFFFF&\move(142,170,152,170,100,3700)}17时05分
